# HIIT Timer 30/40 (`projects/hiit-timer-30-40/`)

30/40 interval timer. Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS (same app pattern as `hiit-timer/`).

## Defaults

- Work: 30 seconds
- Rest: 40 seconds
- Rounds: 8 (user-configurable, `localStorage` keys `hiit-3040-rounds`, `hiit-3040-sound`)
